code: @CacheEntryActivated @CacheEntryCreated @CacheEntryInvalidated @CacheEntryLoaded @CacheEntryModified @CacheEntryPassivated @CacheEntryRemoved @CacheEntryVisited @CacheEntryExpired public void processEvent(CacheEntryEvent<Object, Object> event) {     dispatch(event.getType().toString(), event.isPre(), event.getCache().getName(), event.getKey()). }

private void dispatch(String eventType, boolean isPre, String cacheName, Object key) {     if (isAccepted(eventType)) {         infinispanConsumer.processEvent(eventType, isPre, cacheName, key, null).     } }
